,Recommended,212050,13478999,"Posted: 20 December, 2014",all,lchecket,"This game is fantastic. In a world of pixelated indie games, this one really stands out. If you're the kind of person who loves mystery adventure games, this one is for you. You play as 4 characters, and though only one is given a strong backstory, they each are interesting in their own ways.Some of the puzzles can be a bit tricky, but the story is compelling and the plot really engages you. There are also great scenes of drama and comedy.Don't buy if you're looking for a game with minimal storyline, lots of guns and shiny graphics. Do buy if you're looking for a game that asks interesting moral questions, tells a rich story and humanizes every character."
